name: Paltzer
description:
"Come on Tommy just do it!"
"I am I am, give me a second Jim!"
"I think you're just scared the legends are true"
"Am not!"
"Then draw the sigils!"
"Fine... there! See, its nothing-"
As the Earth began to rumble and split under the poor boys' feet, they realized that they might've been messing with the wrong "nothing".
